 GUILEDART FINISHED THE LAST DEVICE. HE HAD MADE 15OF THEM. HE WASNT SURE HOW 
MANY DESTRONS THEY HAD BUT HE THOUGHT THIS WOULD BE ENOUGH. hE WALKED WITH 
THEM INTO THE CONFRENCE ROOM. "HERE WE GO. pASS ONE TO EACH AND THESE WILL 
WORK AGAINST THE PRED SCANNERA. ALSO I HAVE GOT RECENT INFO ON DARKFATES SHIP 
LCATION. THE PROBE WAS DESTROYED DUE TO INTENCE HEAT BUT THE SHIP IS 
SURRONDED BY LAVA. WE WILL NEED FLYING BOTS TO CARRY THE NON FLYING BOTS OVER 
THE LAVA. THIS MAY COST US AN ADVANTAGE."
